# Data Wrangling and Exploratory Analysis in R

## Project Overview
This project involved sourcing open data from publicly available datasets, importing the data into R, cleaning and transforming raw data, and conducting exploratory analysis.

## Tasks Performed
- Imported external datasets into R
- Cleaned missing/inconsistent values
- Performed data transformation
- Conducted exploratory analysis
- Generated visualisations and summary insights

## Tools Used
- R
- RStudio
- Data Wrangling
- Data Visualization

## Outcome
Developed practical experience in preparing raw datasets for analysis and identifying patterns through exploratory techniques.
